Package ie.gmit.sw

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Database
    An Interface describing how to add and retrieve documents from the DB40 database
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CalculateJaccard
    CalculateJaccard is responsible for determining the jaccard index of an uploaded document compared to all the documents in the database and returning a list of results.
    Document
    An Document Class which are stored in the database.
    DocumentRunner  
    Global
    Called from tge ServiceHandler, this class sets up variables from the web.xml.
    GlobalQueue
    Sets up a Global In and Out Queues so they can be accessed from both the service handlers.
    Results
    Used to store Results, created in the Worker and displayed in the ServicePollHandler.
    ServiceHandler
    Service Handler processes Post Requests from user and handles file upload.
    ServicePollHandler
    ServicePollHandler Class is responsible for displaying the jaccard results back to the user.
    Shingle
    Used to Create a Shingle.
    ShingleWorker
    Creates a list of Shingles and Returns them
    Task
    Used to create a Task object which is then added and removed from the queues.
    Worker
    Created in the ServiceHanlder Constructor, Implements Runnable and spawns a new thread.
